 a summary of what you have planned for tomorrow—and Notifications view shows notifications you missed.</p><figure><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/f0d8a0f2db7dd6b37f61b16dd407dffc.png\" alt=\"Today view showing weather in three locations. Click the Notifications tab to see missed notifications.\" height=\"490\" width=\"285\" originalImageName=\"Art/S0032_NotificationCenter.png\"></figure><div class=\"Alert\"><p class=\"Tip\"><strong class=\"tip\">Tip: </strong>To customize or stop notifications, click the Notifications preferences icon <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/3f28bde7cdd4997ad2a0c1c2d562349b.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"31\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_NCprefs.png\"> in the bottom-right corner of Notification Center.</p></div><div id=\"mchlb29e2dd5\" class=\"Task\"><h2 role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"aria-mchlb29e2dd5\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"Name\">Open Notification Center</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchlb29e2dd5\"><ul class=\"ListSingle\"><li><p>On your Mac, click the Notification Center icon <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/b5a0d77f209598de96f951deddb7d279.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"39\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_NotificationCenter_osx.png\"> in the <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=menu-bar&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL385F1EEA&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14&amp;aside=true\" class=\"xRef Aside\">menu bar</a>, or swipe left with two fingers from the right edge of the trackpad.</p></li></ul></div></div><div id=\"apd3783b0275ec24\" class=\"Task\"><h2 role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"aria-apd3783b0275ec24\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"Name\">Use Today view in Notification Center</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-apd3783b0275ec24\"><ol><li><p>In Notification Center on your Mac, click Today.</p></li><li><p>Click an item in a <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=widget&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL46E845D7&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14&amp;aside=true\" class=\"xRef Aside\">widget</a> to see its details or take an action. </p><p>For example, click an item in the Weather widget to show the hourly and five-day forecasts. Or click a reminder’s checkbox to complete it.</p></li></ol></div></div><div id=\"mchl81797ce0\" class=\"Task\"><h2 role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"aria-mchl81797ce0\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"Name\">Customize Today view Notification Center</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchl81797ce0\"><ol><li><p>In Notification Center on your Mac, click Today.</p></li><li><p>Do any of the following:</p><ul><li><p><em>Customize a widget: </em>Move the pointer over the widget, then click the Info button <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/2ee9a526a71fe4a72de6b253ded36219.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"34\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_Info_osx.png\"> that appears.</p></li><li><p><em>Reorder widgets: </em>Click Edit at the bottom of Today view, then drag a widget up or down.</p></li><li><p><em>Add or remove widgets:  </em>Click Edit (or the new widget count, if shown) at the bottom of Today view. To add an available widget, click its Add button <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/13421e86e694c4548c374f3b1b22367c.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"34\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_AddNotification_osx.png\">. </span>To remove a widget, click its Remove button <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/9811a09781425735c61007fc3eff7d2e.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"34\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_RemovedNotification_osx.png\">; </span>the widget is moved to the list of available widgets. </p></li><li><p><em>Get more widgets: </em>Click Edit at the bottom of Today view, click App Store, then buy or download widgets. For more information about buying and downloading items, see <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=app-store&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=FIR9B2EA074E&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Find, buy, and download apps</a>.</p></li></ul></li></ol></div></div><div id=\"apd467ade90ccd34\" class=\"Task\"><h2 role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"aria-apd467ade90ccd34\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"Name\">Use Notifications view in Notification Center</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-apd467ade90ccd34\"><ol><li><p>In Notification Center on your Mac, click Notifications.</p></li><li><p>Click a notification to open the item in the associated app. For example, click a Mail notification to open the email in Mail.</p></li></ol><p>When you open an item, it’s removed from Notifications view. To remove an item without opening it, move the pointer over it, then click the Clear button <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/a81a56acd2d6621878249802d150fea1.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"28\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_TabClose_osx.png\">. </span>Or click the button for a day to remove all of the day’s notifications.</p></div></div><p>You can turn Night Shift and Do Not Disturb on or off in Notification Center—just swipe down, then click the button.</p><ul><li><p>When you <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-night-shift&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL97BC676D&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">turn on Night Shift</a>, it stays on until midnight, sunrise, the next scheduled time to turn off (based on settings in Night Shift preferences), or you turn it off.</p></li><li><p>When you <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-do-not-disturb&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL999B7C1A&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">turn on Do Not Disturb</a>, it stays on until midnight, the next scheduled time to turn off (based on settings in Notifications preferences), or you turn it off.</p><p>When Do Not Disturb is on, the Notification Center icon in the menu bar is dimmed. You don’t see or hear notifications arrive; they are collected in Notification Center where you can view them later.</p></li></ul><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=receive-pause-or-stop-notifications&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MH40609&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Receive, pause, or stop notifications on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-do-not-disturb&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL999B7C1A&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Use Do Not Disturb on your Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=change-notifications-preferences&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MH40583&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Change Notifications preferences on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-the-find-my-friends-widget&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHLA6CF7F51&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Use the Find My Friends widget on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=change-extensions-preferences&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL8BAF92FE&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Change Extensions preferences on Mac</a></div></body>","tags":[{"type":"audience","refKey":"PUBLIC_USERS","tagPath":"audience/PUBLIC_USERS","title":"Public"}]}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["DisplayVersion/macOS Mojave 10.14","IP-Meta/DesignVersion/DesignVersion2","platform/mac","ContentMode/liveContent","ArchivalStatus/Unarchived","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexON","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexON"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"SupportSearchIndexON","name":"SupportSearchIndexON","englishName":"SupportSearchIndexON","displayName":"SupportSearchIndexON","articleCount":"3950"},{"key":"liveContent","name":"Live Content","englishName":"Live Content","displayName":"Live Content","articleCount":"7864"},{"key":"IP-Meta","name":"IP-Meta","englishName":"IP-Meta","displayName":"IP-Meta","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"Unarchived","name":"Unarchived","englishName":"Unarchived","displayName":"Unarchived","articleCount":"10186"},{"key":"ContentMode","name":"ContentMode","englishName":"ContentMode","displayName":"ContentMode","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ExternalIndexON","name":"ExternalIndexON","englishName":"ExternalIndexON","displayName":"ExternalIndexON","articleCount":"4683"},{"key":"DesignVersion2","name":"DesignVersion 2","englishName":"DesignVersion 2","displayName":"DesignVersion 2","articleCount":"7818"},{"key":"MetaFollow","name":"MetaFollow","englishName":"MetaFollow","displayName":"MetaFollow","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ExternalIndex","name":"ExternalIndex","englishName":"ExternalIndex","displayName":"ExternalIndex","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"DesignVersion","name":"DesignVersion","englishName":"Des